In this project two routers are connected with each other, ip address to pcs are auto assigned using dhcp protocol. 
TO do the routing the following configurations is done in Route 1:
#en 
#config t
#int g 0/0
#ip address 192.168.100.1 255.255.255.0
#no shut
#exit

#ip dhcp pool ABC
#network 192.168.100.0 255.255.255.0
#default-router 192.168.100.1
#ip dhcp excluded-address 192.168.100.1
#ip dhcp pool DEF
#exit

#int g0/0
#ip address 10.0.0.1 255.255.255.252
#no shut
#exit
#ip route 192.168.200.200.0 255.255.255.0 10.0.0.2 (target address)
#exit
#write memory

